// transcriptData.js


const transcriptText = [
  "Distinguished individuals, ladies and gentlemen of the Elite Hoops Club,",
  "",
  "Today, we are united in our efforts on the basketball court.",
  "",
  "Each of us is touched by the thrill of the game, strengthened by choosing to push our limits and reach new heights.",
  "",
  "But allow me to remind you, the road to progress is not without hardships.",
  "",
  "It is in overcoming these obstacles that we grow as athletes.",
  "",
  "So I urge each of you to embrace the journey with commitment and flexibility.",
  "",
  "Let's step out of our comfort zones, support each other as teammates, and strive to make the most out of every dribble, pass, and shot.",
  "",
  "Let's come together as members of the Elite Hoops Club to write a success story.",
  "",
  "Cheer each other on and prove that with patience and insight, anything is possible on the court.",
  "",
  "Thank you."
];

export default transcriptText;
